OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FCloudy with outbreaks of rain
OL,6,Fand drizzle, most persistent through
OL,7,Fthe morning and turning heavy at times
OL,8,Fover the hills. Perhaps some drier
OL,9,Fspells in the afternoon. Windy and
OL,10,Fmild.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FA cloudy evening to come and
OL,13,Foften very windy, particularly around
OL,14,Fcoasts with a risk of gales. Spells of
OL,15,Frain becoming more widespread through
OL,16,Fthe early hours. Mild.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
