OL,3,GNorth West
OL,4,
OL,5,CMonday:FAn unsettled start to the week
OL,6,Fwith wind and rain though some drier
OL,7,Fspells to end the day with lighter
OL,8,Fwinds. Temperatures remain above
OL,9,Faverage for the time of year.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Tuesday to Thursday:FDrier
OL,12,Foverall on Tuesday and Wednesday with
OL,13,Fhigh pressure in charge. A chance of
OL,14,Frain returning on Thursday. Staying
OL,15,Fmild with winds easing.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
